/div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9f90c0847a99712cd04dd5842b761e05e6646ec5","tid":1361778,"uid":131071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"各位連登巴絲 推post 可以直接copy and paste 以下 （如果你認同）：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n集中五大訴求<br />\n1.全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2.撤銷暴動定性<br />\n3.釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n4.全面實行雙普選<br />\n5.成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任(包括警黑勾結元朗恐襲)<br />\n<br />\n7.27 支持元朗居民,反黑鄉<br />\nBe Water<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力 齊上齊落<br />\n不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆 不譴責 不撤不散<br />\n提防三毛 五毛"},{"pid":"315cdb756ce96b7917acd9f1f7b3a5bdc672aea5","tid":1361778,"uid":131071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc78e2318918fecfee8f7a7de66a618a801ac201","tid":1361778,"uid":131071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b8122be46e1c07f137e89798c502512dab06a9","tid":1361778,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90ce04ddca5b73e8aca4c277990fdac79dfd7d70","tid":1361778,"uid":269945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:44:57.000Z","msg":"有不反對通知書了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"Source ？"},{"pid":"6dbb1d9a05fe37dcd931d92fe99e255a687715de","tid":1361778,"uid":131071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c82054902918d42b7136e2653507f58a2d2ce87","tid":1361778,"uid":131071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}